Flowcase is a free and completely open-source alternative to Kasm Workspaces, enabling secure container streaming for your applications.

it is a web application that allows you to stream your docker containers to your browser.

It is made with flask and docker.

A "Droplet" is equivalent to a Workspace in Kasm Workspaces. it can be a docker image or a guacamole container.

Users can create droplets, or add existing droplets from a registry.